 What This Tool Does:
 Azure Data factory and fabric data factory are used for data integeration and orcehstration

 Its commanly used to:
 . Copy data from source to distination
 . schedule daily or hourly pipeline
 . Pass parameters into reusable pipeline
 . Trigger databricks notebooks or stored procedures 
 . Monitor pipeline success and failure

 Activity:
 an activity is one task inside a pipeline
Example:
. Copy activity
. Lookup activity
. if condition
. foreach
. web activity
. notebook activity

Linked Service:

A Linked service is a connection details to a system
example:
Azure sql database conection
ADLS gen2 connection
rest API connection
databricks connection

Dataset: A dataset points to the actual data location or structure
Example: 
sql table: dbo.orders
ADLS file path: raw/ecommerce/orders/2026/26/06/orders.csv

Trigger: A trigger start a pipeline
Example: 
Run daily at 1pm
run hourly
run when a file arrrive

